data.description: Welcome to Stonewood Crossings! Wait until you see this huge and well-maintained home that boasts a spacious 2,846 square feet of heated living space. The 4 bedroom and 2 baths home offers plenty of room for both relaxation and entertainment. The living room and kitchen offer ample space for hosting guests or enjoying a cozy evening in. The kitchen comes complete with modern appliances and plenty of counter and cabinet space, including 2 pantries for all your culinary needs! The 4 bedrooms offer plenty of room for rest and relaxation, with comfortable carpeting and plenty of natural light. The oversized Master suite has all the space you could need. A sliding barn door leads to the completely remodeled en suite with his and hers closets and tiled walk in shower. The fenced in backyard with it's avocado tree is a relaxing oasis featuring a fully screened in patio creating even more space for entertaining. Located in the sought-after Stonewood Crossings neighborhood, this home is a mere 30 minutes from Disney World and just minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this stunning home yours!
